WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.050 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 27]

02:03.250 --> 02:05.430
[Shanghai Hongkou District
Central Hospital]

02:05.450 --> 02:08.259
[Gastroscopy Diagnosis Report]

02:08.280 --> 02:10.759
[Diagnosis: Massive protruding lesion
at the cardia]

02:10.789 --> 02:13.720
[[Highly suspected malignant
characteristics]]

02:16.500 --> 02:20.079
[Ke Wenxue]

02:16.840 --> 02:17.640
Hey everyone,

02:17.800 --> 02:19.800
I heard Purong is about to enter
a close collaboration

02:19.800 --> 02:20.930
with Jiang Zhichun.

02:20.460 --> 02:21.400
[Luo Qingping]

02:21.470 --> 02:22.430
What's going on?

02:22.010 --> 02:22.829
[Yin Xiang]

02:23.240 --> 02:24.430
You guys didn't know?

02:24.430 --> 02:26.490
Mr. Ji and Jiang Zhichun are a couple.

02:26.800 --> 02:27.520
Wow,

02:27.680 --> 02:28.840
a power couple team-up,

02:28.840 --> 02:29.960
total double A energy.

02:29.960 --> 02:30.870
It's raining.

02:31.120 --> 02:32.850
Hurry and bring the laundry in.

02:36.079 --> 02:37.280
Focus on your work,

02:37.400 --> 02:38.450
Xu Miyu.

02:43.730 --> 02:45.460
Quick, get the clothes inside.

02:48.340 --> 02:50.190
Why is it raining again?

03:10.420 --> 03:11.290
Coming.

03:16.840 --> 03:17.750
Lu Xiaoyan?

03:18.030 --> 03:18.820
What's the matter?

03:18.820 --> 03:19.660
Ms. Xu,

03:19.680 --> 03:21.079
does our hotel have any discount policies

03:21.079 --> 03:22.630
during the college entrance exam period?

03:22.630 --> 03:23.310
Come in and talk first.

03:23.310 --> 03:23.930
Sure.

03:25.470 --> 03:27.710
My cousin is taking the college
entrance exam this year,

03:27.710 --> 03:29.630
and his test center is right
near our Purong Hotel.

03:29.630 --> 03:32.110
It's a newly added exam site, I heard.

03:32.150 --> 03:32.910
My aunt was thinking

03:32.910 --> 03:34.840
of booking a room here

03:34.840 --> 03:36.910
for him during the exams,

03:37.120 --> 03:39.400
but she's worried it'll be too expensive.

03:39.400 --> 03:41.240
So she asked me to check

03:41.240 --> 03:43.030
if there are any special offers.

03:43.030 --> 03:45.910
They're just regular working-class folks,

03:46.190 --> 03:47.310
you know how it is, Ms. Xu.

03:47.310 --> 03:48.280
I understand.

03:48.750 --> 03:50.470
Is that new exam site

03:50.470 --> 03:52.240
the Xinhua Finance and Economics School

03:52.240 --> 03:53.500
over on Yanghuai Road?

03:54.030 --> 03:55.280
You already knew.

03:58.750 --> 03:59.870
I was actually planning

03:59.870 --> 04:01.470
to head over there tomorrow
to check it out.

04:01.470 --> 04:02.840
Look, it's right here.

04:03.360 --> 04:04.240
If

04:04.240 --> 04:06.120
the scale and location work out well,

04:06.120 --> 04:07.400
I want to submit an application
to the hotel

04:07.400 --> 04:09.190
for a special discount for exam-takers.

04:09.190 --> 04:10.400
That'd be amazing!

04:10.630 --> 04:11.960
Take me with you then.

04:11.960 --> 04:14.030
I wanna scope out the exam site
for my cousin too.

04:14.030 --> 04:14.680
Deal.

04:22.800 --> 04:23.630
Here we are.

04:23.700 --> 04:28.310
[Xinhua Finance and Economics School
Police Service Office]

04:26.800 --> 04:28.510
It only took us

04:28.370 --> 04:30.990
[Timer]

04:28.920 --> 04:30.000
eleven minutes on foot
from the hotel lobby

04:30.000 --> 04:31.190
to get here.

04:31.190 --> 04:31.950
That walking distance

04:31.950 --> 04:33.240
is pretty ideal.

04:33.690 --> 04:36.420
But what if the guest room elevators
get crowded?

04:36.630 --> 04:37.750
If that happens,

04:37.750 --> 04:38.800
we'll make

04:38.800 --> 04:40.330
a staggered schedule plan,

04:41.030 --> 04:42.430
assign specific

04:42.430 --> 04:43.770
elevator time slots by floor.

04:43.770 --> 04:46.090
We'll need the Housekeeping team
to cooperate,

04:46.090 --> 04:47.750
have attendants on each floor help
keep order during that time.

04:47.750 --> 04:50.010
help maintain order when the time comes.

04:50.110 --> 04:51.159
Ms. Xu,

04:51.190 --> 04:52.460
you're so thoughtful.

04:52.510 --> 04:54.040
The college entrance exam only comes
once in a lifetime,

04:54.040 --> 04:56.000
it's every family's top priority.

04:56.480 --> 04:59.210
We should always go the extra mile
for our guests.

04:59.720 --> 05:00.310
Let's go.

05:02.460 --> 05:03.790
Who are you looking for?

05:04.590 --> 05:06.990
Sir, please let us take
a quick look inside.

05:07.000 --> 05:08.430
We just wanna walk around for a minute.

05:08.430 --> 05:09.240
Walk around?

05:09.240 --> 05:10.820
If anything goes missing in here,
I'll get blamed for it.

05:10.820 --> 05:11.680
This is my sister.

05:11.680 --> 05:12.750
She's taking the college
entrance exam soon.

05:12.750 --> 05:14.510
I wanted to bring her to get
familiar with the area,

05:14.510 --> 05:15.680
so she won't get

05:15.680 --> 05:16.870
too nervous on exam day

05:16.870 --> 05:18.160
and mess up her mood.

05:18.510 --> 05:19.160
Exactly.

05:19.180 --> 05:20.800
We just wanna see the classrooms

05:20.800 --> 05:22.360
and get familiar with the route.

05:22.360 --> 05:23.300
Exam-takers, huh?

05:23.300 --> 05:24.460
Can't be too careful with that.

05:24.460 --> 05:25.920
Wait a second, I'll unlock the door.

05:25.920 --> 05:26.920
Thank you so much.

05:28.200 --> 05:32.610
[Reminder: No unauthorized entry
for outsiders]

05:31.560 --> 05:32.510
Come on, this way.

05:32.510 --> 05:33.159
Let's go.

05:40.630 --> 05:41.430
Director Bai.

05:41.480 --> 05:42.040
Save whatever

05:42.040 --> 05:43.190
you need to say for after my meeting.

05:43.190 --> 05:43.990
I'm gonna be late.

05:43.990 --> 05:46.320
This might come in handy for your meeting.

05:47.680 --> 05:49.430
I put this together over
the past few days,

05:49.430 --> 05:51.090
a full research report on this year's
college entrance exam sites.

05:51.090 --> 05:52.150
Please take a look.

05:52.820 --> 05:53.750
[Shanghai College Entrance Exam Site
Research Report]

05:53.750 --> 05:54.670
[Table of Contents]

05:53.830 --> 05:54.750
Five new exam sites

05:54.750 --> 05:56.280
have been added across the city this year,

05:56.280 --> 05:58.190
and one's located right next
to our hotel —

05:58.190 --> 05:59.620
Xinhua Finance and Economics School.

05:59.620 --> 06:00.800
I've already checked the location
in person,

06:00.800 --> 06:01.720
the information is confirmed,

06:01.720 --> 06:03.300
and they're already setting up
the exam classrooms.

06:03.300 --> 06:04.860
What does any of this

06:04.880 --> 06:06.340
have to do with my meeting?

06:07.110 --> 06:09.260
These people are all potential customers.

06:09.260 --> 06:10.840
Exam students, their parents,

06:10.840 --> 06:12.680
even the exam supervisors.

06:13.230 --> 06:14.310
Didn't Mr. Ji urge

06:14.310 --> 06:15.720
all management staff
to brainstorm new business ideas?

06:15.720 --> 06:17.920
This is ridiculous for
potential customers.

06:17.920 --> 06:18.870
Let me tell you,

06:18.890 --> 06:21.560
people buried in exam stress
have nothing on their minds but the test.

06:21.560 --> 06:23.510
Even if you offered them a luxury
five-star hotel stay,

06:23.510 --> 06:24.750
they wouldn't be in the mood for it.

06:24.750 --> 06:27.430
Plus, there are tons of
budget hotels nearby.

06:27.430 --> 06:28.830
We can't compete with them

06:28.830 --> 06:30.310
for exam-taker business.

06:30.800 --> 06:32.390
Regular families on a budget

06:32.390 --> 06:35.250
aren't gonna splurge on a fancy hotel
for the exams.

06:35.720 --> 06:36.500
Director Bai,

06:36.500 --> 06:38.500
this isn't just wishful thinking.

06:38.560 --> 06:38.950
Recently,

06:38.950 --> 06:39.920
we've been getting booking inquiries

06:39.920 --> 06:41.000
one after another

06:41.000 --> 06:42.810
for stays during the exam period.

06:42.810 --> 06:43.430
And this is all

06:43.430 --> 06:45.480
without any official discounts

06:45.480 --> 06:47.500
or promotional ads launched yet.

06:47.530 --> 06:50.340
I believe there's huge untapped
business potential here.

06:50.340 --> 06:51.630
Shi Huanhuan compiled all

06:51.630 --> 06:53.040
the reservation data,

06:53.040 --> 06:54.100
please take a look.

06:54.210 --> 06:56.890
[Purong Hotel Walk-In Reservation Summary]

06:56.270 --> 06:59.000
That's only a dozen bookings total.

06:59.000 --> 07:00.810
Not even enough to fill one floor.

07:00.810 --> 07:02.070
And we can't even confirm

07:02.070 --> 07:04.220
they're all exam families.

07:04.240 --> 07:07.360
This idea's not half as good as Mr. Ji's
rain-viewing group.

07:07.360 --> 07:08.000
Ms. Xu,

07:08.510 --> 07:09.580
it's not worth the effort.

07:09.580 --> 07:11.040
I appreciate the initiative though.

07:11.040 --> 07:13.440
Come find me later if you
have better ideas.

07:13.560 --> 07:14.480
I'm seriously running late

07:14.480 --> 07:15.340
for my meeting.

07:19.770 --> 07:20.990
We'll talk later.

07:21.150 --> 07:22.550
Take care, Director Bai.

07:28.320 --> 07:30.720
[Purong Hotel, Enduring
Rivers, Lasting Glory]

07:30.740 --> 07:34.340
[Purong Hotel, Always By Your Side]

07:33.070 --> 07:34.120
In my opinion,

07:34.600 --> 07:38.190
Mr. Ji, there’s no need for you
to worry too much.

07:39.310 --> 07:41.750
Hasn't the rain-viewing group checked in
these past two days?

07:41.750 --> 07:43.870
You're right, occupancy is way better

07:43.870 --> 07:44.870
than it was

07:44.870 --> 07:47.120
this same time last year.

07:47.120 --> 07:48.090
Besides,

07:48.870 --> 07:49.950
even the best scenic spots

07:49.950 --> 07:51.190
have off and peak seasons.

07:51.190 --> 07:51.870
Right?

07:52.520 --> 07:53.310
Our hotel

07:53.310 --> 07:55.120
operates in the same cycle.

07:55.140 --> 07:55.830
And,

07:55.980 --> 07:56.659
it's also

07:57.400 --> 07:58.760
rainy season right now,

07:59.500 --> 08:00.850
slower business is totally normal.

08:00.850 --> 08:02.580
Director Huang's right.

08:02.750 --> 08:05.120
Our hotel's current operating state

08:05.120 --> 08:06.580
isn't so much a bottleneck

08:07.000 --> 08:08.120
as it's just

08:08.310 --> 08:11.000
hitting a regular seasonal low point.

08:11.560 --> 08:13.750
Other hotels are also...

08:13.750 --> 08:16.660
Off-season management doesn't
mean we just let things slide.

08:16.660 --> 08:18.790
Tourism fluctuates with the weather,

08:18.800 --> 08:20.460
but business doesn't have to.

08:20.920 --> 08:21.680
Beyond tourist stays,

08:21.680 --> 08:22.900
our hotel can host

08:23.390 --> 08:25.710
corporate events,

08:26.510 --> 08:28.240
and offer premium fine dining.

08:29.820 --> 08:32.490
I want everyone to think outside the box

08:32.840 --> 08:35.039
and actively explore new
business opportunities.

08:35.039 --> 08:36.150
[Dad, I miss you.]

08:35.440 --> 08:37.970
Alright then, since Mr. Ji
put it that way…

08:37.940 --> 08:39.700
[Daughter]

08:38.120 --> 08:40.120
We need to chase new
business opportunities.

08:40.120 --> 08:41.000
Director Qian,

08:41.510 --> 08:42.909
do you have any insights?

08:48.410 --> 08:49.210
Director Bai.

08:49.810 --> 08:50.690
Director Bai!

08:54.440 --> 08:55.000
Here.

08:55.550 --> 08:56.350
What's wrong?

08:57.020 --> 08:58.020
Director Bai.

08:58.930 --> 09:01.710
Everyone's waiting for your input.

09:01.840 --> 09:02.630
Me?

09:04.640 --> 09:05.700
Alright.

09:06.000 --> 09:06.840
Let's not

09:07.030 --> 09:08.820
pressure Director Bai.

09:09.000 --> 09:09.750
After all,

09:10.240 --> 09:13.500
it's not the Front Office's
place to worry about this.

09:16.750 --> 09:17.750
To be honest,

09:17.960 --> 09:19.940
I've been thinking about something lately.

09:19.940 --> 09:20.570
Go ahead.

09:21.540 --> 09:23.030
What if we tapped into

09:23.360 --> 09:26.360
the college entrance exam crowd
for new business?

09:28.580 --> 09:29.120
Look how

09:29.120 --> 09:30.990
desperate we've gotten.

09:32.110 --> 09:32.960
Director Bai,

09:33.320 --> 09:34.000
the college entrance exam,

09:34.000 --> 09:36.630
high school students aren't tour groups.

09:37.500 --> 09:38.390
They're not

09:38.410 --> 09:41.070
here for a vacation right before
their big exam.

09:42.110 --> 09:43.200
Though you never know,

09:43.200 --> 09:45.080
maybe this year's exam essay prompt

09:45.080 --> 09:46.780
will be all about Purong Hotel.

09:46.780 --> 09:48.000
After all, our hotel boasts

09:48.000 --> 09:50.240
nearly half a century of
remarkable history.

09:50.240 --> 09:51.000
Right?

09:51.000 --> 09:53.260
Mr. Huang, I've done thorough research.

09:53.670 --> 09:54.360
Mr. Ji,

09:54.420 --> 09:55.260
look at

09:55.280 --> 09:58.400
what you've driven us to.

09:58.680 --> 10:01.390
Even Front Office Director Bai Yongjun

10:01.410 --> 10:02.970
is doing market research now.

10:02.970 --> 10:04.170
That's a great thing.

10:04.200 --> 10:06.660
It just shows everyone's full
of potential.

10:07.660 --> 10:08.400
Go on,

10:09.040 --> 10:09.900
Director Bai.

10:09.980 --> 10:10.840
I...

10:12.400 --> 10:13.000
Well…

10:13.670 --> 10:15.180
I found out a new exam site

10:15.200 --> 10:17.000
was added this year,

10:17.020 --> 10:18.690
right next to our hotel.

10:19.090 --> 10:20.150
How close exactly?

10:20.290 --> 10:21.090
Pretty close,

10:22.440 --> 10:23.680
not far at all.

10:24.490 --> 10:26.560
What's the name of the new site?

10:27.040 --> 10:27.870
It's…

10:30.480 --> 10:32.480
Where did you get this information?

10:32.840 --> 10:34.290
Municipal Education Commission website?

10:34.290 --> 10:36.520
Exam Authority official site?

10:37.750 --> 10:39.550
How many exam seats does it have?

10:39.670 --> 10:41.870
What's the background of the students?

10:47.470 --> 10:48.730
It's fine, Director Bai,

10:48.730 --> 10:49.850
don't be nervous.

10:49.880 --> 10:50.750
Did you do this research alone,

10:50.750 --> 10:51.840
or with help?

10:51.840 --> 10:53.840
We collaborated on it.

10:53.870 --> 10:55.000
There's another team member

10:55.000 --> 10:56.460
who knows all the details.

10:56.840 --> 10:57.960
I can go get her.

10:59.200 --> 11:00.030
Please do.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.320
Send Ms. Xu to

11:09.320 --> 11:10.150
the conference room immediately.

11:10.150 --> 11:10.810
Chop, chop!

11:11.000 --> 11:12.060
We're all waiting.

11:24.210 --> 11:24.970
Ms. Xu,

11:25.440 --> 11:26.500
this might actually work out!

11:26.500 --> 11:27.960
Just wait for my good news.

11:28.060 --> 11:28.990
You've got this.

11:34.220 --> 11:36.470
[2025 Shanghai College Entrance Exam]

11:36.490 --> 11:37.870
[Comprehensive Analysis Report]

11:38.240 --> 11:40.050
[Current Exam Site Distribution]

11:45.840 --> 11:48.570
How long is the walk from
our hotel to the exam site?

11:48.570 --> 11:50.290
11 minutes from the lobby.

11:53.860 --> 11:54.910
You've visited the site in person?

11:54.910 --> 11:55.950
Yes,

11:56.140 --> 11:57.360
I checked it out myself.

11:57.360 --> 11:59.250
The new site is Xinhua Finance and
Economics Technical School.

11:59.250 --> 12:00.360
30 classrooms total,

12:00.360 --> 12:01.880
30 seats per classroom,

12:01.900 --> 12:03.600
900 exam-takers in total.

12:03.600 --> 12:04.200
Exactly.

12:04.200 --> 12:05.320
Once Ms. Xu told me the details,

12:05.320 --> 12:07.850
I knew this was a solid
business opportunity.

12:09.840 --> 12:10.960
What's your plan for execution?

12:10.960 --> 12:12.670
First, offer discounted room rates,

12:12.670 --> 12:14.550
then launch customized exclusive services.

12:14.550 --> 12:15.910
How steep of a discount?

12:16.150 --> 12:17.510
Half price off regular rates.

12:17.510 --> 12:18.670
I strongly oppose that.

12:18.670 --> 12:19.960
Slashing prices in half

12:19.960 --> 12:21.080
would turn Purong Hotel

12:21.080 --> 12:22.440
into a budget motel.

12:22.460 --> 12:24.260
Forget about brand reputation,

12:24.440 --> 12:25.720
where would our profit

12:26.550 --> 12:27.480
margin come from?

12:27.480 --> 12:29.080
Brand image is manageable.

12:29.100 --> 12:31.320
Let me address the profit issue first.

12:31.550 --> 12:32.670
Our hotel

12:32.670 --> 12:34.360
has 368 guest rooms in total,

12:34.360 --> 12:35.200
Over 90%

12:35.250 --> 12:37.330
of which are vacant right now.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.240
Daily

12:38.260 --> 12:39.270
operating costs per room,

12:39.270 --> 12:40.600
including staff expenses,

12:40.600 --> 12:42.320
are roughly 100 RMB.

12:42.340 --> 12:43.840
Even at half price,

12:43.840 --> 12:46.030
exam families would still pay
600 RMB per night.

12:46.030 --> 12:48.320
That leaves us 500 RMB in
net profit per room.

12:48.320 --> 12:50.270
The margin isn't huge,
but it's far better

12:50.270 --> 12:51.360
than leaving rooms empty.

12:51.360 --> 12:52.030
Right?

12:52.320 --> 12:53.320
Ms. Xu,

12:53.550 --> 12:55.500
your math is oversimplified.

12:55.600 --> 12:57.530
You're ignoring marketing costs.

12:57.670 --> 13:00.600
Once we lock in this promotion plan,

13:00.670 --> 13:02.270
advertising and promotion fees

13:02.270 --> 13:03.910
will skyrocket.

13:04.440 --> 13:05.480
Not necessarily.

13:05.840 --> 13:07.910
We're in the digital live-stream era now.

13:07.910 --> 13:10.600
Our hotel has an annual
partnership package

13:10.600 --> 13:11.840
with Dianjiangchun's live-stream team.

13:11.840 --> 13:12.720
I suggest

13:12.720 --> 13:13.960
we start

13:13.960 --> 13:15.440
with short live-stream

13:15.440 --> 13:16.480
promotions

13:16.480 --> 13:18.030
to test market response.

13:18.200 --> 13:19.440
If results are promising,

13:19.440 --> 13:21.040
we can scale up paid ads later.

13:21.040 --> 13:23.030
No need for massive

13:23.080 --> 13:24.140
upfront spending.

13:24.250 --> 13:25.480
I understand

13:25.480 --> 13:26.670
basic ad strategy,

13:26.690 --> 13:27.930
but do you realize

13:27.960 --> 13:31.070
our target audience is less than
a thousand people?

13:31.270 --> 13:33.510
Dianjiangchun has tens of millions

13:33.510 --> 13:34.910
of followers nationwide.

13:34.910 --> 13:36.720
The targeting accuracy will
be abysmally low.

13:36.720 --> 13:37.550
You said it yourself,

13:37.550 --> 13:38.600
we can't

13:38.600 --> 13:40.550
go all-in at first.

13:40.550 --> 13:41.720
So tell me,

13:41.720 --> 13:44.150
what's the initial budget?

13:44.320 --> 13:46.150
What's the customer acquisition cost?

13:46.150 --> 13:49.150
This is nothing but looking for
a needle in a haystack.

13:49.670 --> 13:50.550
Director Qian,

13:50.800 --> 13:52.150
your points make perfect sense

13:52.150 --> 13:54.360
in standard business logic,

13:54.630 --> 13:56.740
but my proposal has solid
reasoning behind it.

13:56.740 --> 13:58.440
We’ve run multiple joint promotions

13:58.440 --> 14:00.150
with Dianjiangchun before,

14:00.150 --> 14:01.360
and the results were consistently strong.

14:01.360 --> 14:02.880
Platform big data shows

14:02.910 --> 14:04.600
the core audience interested
in our hotel promotions

14:04.600 --> 14:05.360
are

14:05.360 --> 14:06.480
middle-aged residents

14:06.480 --> 14:08.670
aged 40 to 50 in Shanghai.

14:08.790 --> 14:11.510
And this group overlaps heavily
with our target customers—

14:11.510 --> 14:14.440
families of exam-takers.

14:14.670 --> 14:16.550
By tagging our promotions with

14:16.550 --> 14:17.790
“Purong Hotel”

14:17.790 --> 14:19.670
and “college entrance exam”,

14:19.750 --> 14:20.440
I think

14:20.440 --> 14:22.030
we'll drastically boost

14:22.030 --> 14:23.290
targeting precision.

14:24.320 --> 14:25.970
Indeed, you're right on

14:26.080 --> 14:28.200
our audience size. While it may be small

14:28.200 --> 14:29.860
and the hit rate may be low,

14:29.880 --> 14:31.480
we can't overlook

14:31.480 --> 14:33.960
parent group communities.

14:33.980 --> 14:36.480
If we deliver truly valuable services

14:36.480 --> 14:38.320
for exam families,

14:38.350 --> 14:39.690
one satisfied customer

14:40.080 --> 14:42.080
will spread the word to dozens more.

14:51.840 --> 14:53.560
What customized services
are you proposing?

14:53.560 --> 14:56.200
First, designate exclusive floors

14:56.200 --> 14:57.200
for exam families

14:57.200 --> 14:59.000
to guarantee a quiet, undisturbed stay.

14:59.000 --> 14:59.790
Second,

14:59.790 --> 15:00.750
provide nutritionally balanced

15:00.750 --> 15:02.540
meal sets with diverse flavors.

15:02.540 --> 15:04.140
We'll take daily headcounts

15:04.270 --> 15:05.380
for on-demand catering,

15:05.380 --> 15:07.740
cutting kitchen food waste

15:07.850 --> 15:10.150
while ensuring proper nutrition
for students.

15:10.150 --> 15:11.070
Third,

15:11.120 --> 15:12.980
adjust service hours:

15:13.040 --> 15:15.050
serve breakfast one hour earlier,

15:15.080 --> 15:17.010
and add late-night snack service.

15:17.050 --> 15:19.530
Plus, open our gym and swimming pool

15:19.570 --> 15:20.910
during the college entrance examination,

15:20.910 --> 15:23.080
or free to all exam-takers
during the exam period.

15:23.080 --> 15:25.880
Ms. Xu, are you saying

15:25.900 --> 15:27.380
we need to restructure the entire hotel

15:27.380 --> 15:29.820
just to cater to these students?

15:29.840 --> 15:32.650
What about our regular guests?

15:32.680 --> 15:34.320
How many rooms

15:34.340 --> 15:36.600
are currently occupied in Housekeeping?

15:36.600 --> 15:38.960
Only 80 rooms at most.

15:38.990 --> 15:41.110
That's a mere 20% occupancy rate.

15:42.440 --> 15:44.960
Can you guarantee filling 3 full floors?

15:45.150 --> 15:46.550
3 floors won't be enough.

15:46.550 --> 15:47.480
I'm aiming for 6.

15:52.320 --> 15:55.300
Where did you get this

15:55.320 --> 15:57.120
newfound confidence?

15:57.360 --> 15:59.080
It's reasonable math, actually.

15:59.080 --> 15:59.960
6 floors

16:00.030 --> 16:01.720
equal 180 rooms,

16:01.750 --> 16:04.060
only 20% of the 900
total exam-takers.

16:04.080 --> 16:06.600
My projection is quite conservative.

16:06.630 --> 16:08.420
High schools across all
11 Shanghai districts

16:08.420 --> 16:10.740
are reassigned to mixed exam sites.

16:10.840 --> 16:12.600
The closest high school to
Xinhua Finance School

16:12.600 --> 16:13.960
is still 5.4 km away,

16:13.960 --> 16:14.550
and

16:14.550 --> 16:16.860
they all have to travel through the
heavily congested Old Zhongshan Road.

16:16.860 --> 16:17.770
I estimate

16:17.800 --> 16:19.730
over 80% of these 900 students

16:19.750 --> 16:22.450
will need nearby hotel accommodations.

16:22.770 --> 16:24.590
I kept my forecast modest

16:24.610 --> 16:26.460
to account for competing hotels

16:26.600 --> 16:28.650
and diverse customer needs.

16:28.710 --> 16:29.630
So,

16:29.710 --> 16:30.710
I believe

16:30.740 --> 16:33.000
6 floors is a completely realistic goal.

16:38.670 --> 16:39.550
Really?

16:39.960 --> 16:40.840
Absolutely.

16:40.980 --> 16:43.600
Students with a valid exam
admission ticket and ID

16:43.600 --> 16:45.540
get 50% off.

16:45.570 --> 16:47.080
Stacked with staff discount perks,

16:47.080 --> 16:48.910
our rates will be cheaper than

16:48.910 --> 16:50.370
local three-star hotels.

16:50.900 --> 16:52.690
Thank you so much, Ms. Xu!

16:52.720 --> 16:54.780
I'll book my cousin's room right now.

16:55.190 --> 16:56.540
Hold on,

16:56.570 --> 16:58.000
this is still unofficial news.

16:58.000 --> 16:59.560
The policy hasn't been fully approved yet.

16:59.560 --> 17:02.530
If you wait for official confirmation,
it'll be too late.

17:02.530 --> 17:03.250
Ms. Xu.

17:07.730 --> 17:08.530
It's crooked.

17:09.770 --> 17:10.380
Thank you.

17:30.380 --> 17:31.100
Going up?

17:47.270 --> 17:49.670
The exam room promotion idea is brilliant.

17:49.790 --> 17:51.420
It'll definitely boost

17:51.440 --> 17:52.660
hotel performance.

17:52.680 --> 17:54.880
Thank you for your recognition, Mr. Ji.

17:58.720 --> 18:00.280
Have you decided

18:00.310 --> 18:02.770
which team to partner with
for the campaign?

18:03.270 --> 18:04.070
The Sales team

18:04.070 --> 18:05.790
is already in talks
with Dianjiangchun's crew

18:05.790 --> 18:08.450
to confirm schedules and
collaboration terms.

18:10.370 --> 18:12.680
Partnering with Ms. Jiang
is a solid choice.

18:12.680 --> 18:13.550
Online fans

18:13.550 --> 18:15.750
have been buzzing about
you two lately,

18:16.200 --> 18:19.730
everyone's waiting for your next
public appearance together.

18:23.870 --> 18:25.110
Our relationship

18:25.960 --> 18:28.360
is strictly professional collaboration,

18:28.790 --> 18:29.590
nothing more.

18:30.640 --> 18:32.270
Why keep

18:32.270 --> 18:34.200
your connection a secret at first?

18:35.290 --> 18:37.550
Did you and Ms. Jiang know
each other beforehand?

18:37.550 --> 18:38.590
We

18:40.270 --> 18:41.930
were university classmates.

18:43.220 --> 18:44.680
I didn't mean to overstep.

18:53.590 --> 18:54.830
So,

18:55.690 --> 18:58.000
this is what's bothering you?

18:59.400 --> 19:00.340
Not at all.

19:00.530 --> 19:02.220
Why would I care about that?

19:02.450 --> 19:03.980
It has nothing to do with me.

19:13.870 --> 19:15.490
♪ Life is full of ♪

19:16.650 --> 19:19.130
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

19:20.490 --> 19:24.340
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

19:25.170 --> 19:26.410
Thank you, Ji Feng.

19:25.930 --> 19:27.930
♪ All those confusions ♪

19:28.520 --> 19:32.240
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

19:30.220 --> 19:32.650
Did you and Ms. Jiang know
each other beforehand?

19:32.650 --> 19:33.960
Did you and Jiang Zhichun

19:33.120 --> 19:37.120
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

19:33.960 --> 19:35.550
only ever have a work relationship?

19:35.550 --> 19:37.030
Why keep

19:37.030 --> 19:38.920
your connection a secret at first?

19:38.920 --> 19:39.880
Are you still upset with me?

19:39.370 --> 19:41.830
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

19:39.880 --> 19:40.440
Yes,

19:41.000 --> 19:42.020
I am upset.

19:42.550 --> 19:44.310
I'm tired of being the person
who forgives

19:43.050 --> 19:45.250
♪ Don't look back ♪

19:44.310 --> 19:46.160
and forgets the second someone says sorry.

19:46.160 --> 19:47.820
♪ I've already learned ♪

19:48.560 --> 19:52.360
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

19:53.300 --> 19:54.940
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

19:55.370 --> 19:59.750
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

20:00.510 --> 20:03.300
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

20:04.170 --> 20:06.690
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

20:07.310 --> 20:09.230
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

20:30.680 --> 20:31.400
Mr. Qian,

20:31.620 --> 20:35.280
Let me take charge of the live stream
for our exam-week promotion.

20:35.920 --> 20:36.780
Sit down first.

20:37.440 --> 20:38.570
Come on, have a seat.

20:41.640 --> 20:42.760
Ms. Lu,

20:43.440 --> 20:45.110
your health right now

20:45.550 --> 20:47.200
isn't fit for field work.

20:48.160 --> 20:50.000
You know perfectly well how draining

20:50.000 --> 20:51.200
livestreaming is.

20:51.200 --> 20:53.110
You can't handle the whole session alone.

20:53.110 --> 20:54.920
I can handle it.

20:54.920 --> 20:55.640
Look.

20:57.350 --> 20:59.700
I can still work in high heels.

20:59.720 --> 21:01.230
I've been pregnant for months,

21:01.230 --> 21:03.290
and when have I ever let my work slide?

21:03.560 --> 21:06.020
I can work through any
physical discomfort.

21:06.070 --> 21:07.470
Just give me this chance.

21:08.880 --> 21:09.700
Ms. Lu,

21:09.920 --> 21:12.590
it's not that I'm holding you back.

21:13.160 --> 21:14.030
The truth is,

21:15.590 --> 21:18.350
this project is personally
overseen by Mr. Ji.

21:18.400 --> 21:19.270
I'm worried…

21:19.270 --> 21:21.680
Then put in a good word
for me with Mr. Ji.

21:21.680 --> 21:24.070
I'm not trying to curry favor with him.

21:24.560 --> 21:26.310
I just won't let our Sales Department

21:26.310 --> 21:27.880
lose to the Front Office.

21:27.950 --> 21:30.190
This is our sales performance.

21:30.350 --> 21:32.210
I'm going to fight to take it back.

21:33.350 --> 21:34.070
Mr. Qian.

21:34.790 --> 21:37.030
I've always been on your side.

21:37.190 --> 21:38.010
When it

21:38.350 --> 21:39.270
comes to online sales and livestreaming,

21:39.270 --> 21:41.400
no one at Purong Hotel knows
this business better than me.

21:41.400 --> 21:43.160
My husband works in the travel industry

21:43.160 --> 21:44.550
and partners with new media companies

21:44.550 --> 21:45.680
all the time.

21:45.790 --> 21:46.400
I know exactly

21:46.400 --> 21:48.350
how to do the preliminary research

21:48.350 --> 21:49.650
for this new line of business.

21:49.650 --> 21:50.350
Mr. Qian,

21:50.960 --> 21:52.200
give me this opportunity.

21:52.200 --> 21:53.400
I won't let you down.

21:57.590 --> 21:59.250
Don't push yourself too hard.

22:00.680 --> 22:01.850
Just take it easy.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.810
Thank you, Mr. Qian.

22:17.950 --> 22:18.700
Let's go.

22:19.040 --> 22:19.810
Let's go.

22:19.840 --> 22:20.970
Time to get off work.

22:21.680 --> 22:22.350
Let's go, Zhenzhen.

22:22.350 --> 22:24.280
Can't. I've got overtime tonight.

22:24.840 --> 22:25.770
Wait for me a sec.

22:30.790 --> 22:31.870
[Nie Yucheng]

22:36.220 --> 22:37.200
Hey honey,

22:38.400 --> 22:40.400
I really can't make it home tonight.

22:40.830 --> 22:42.290
We'll talk when I get back.

22:47.700 --> 22:49.360
[Outpatient Building]

22:52.810 --> 22:54.720
Nie Yucheng, come in.

22:59.710 --> 23:00.710
Wait a minute.

23:02.200 --> 23:02.770
Mom.

23:05.030 --> 23:06.090
Where is Zhenzhen?

23:08.380 --> 23:09.340
She didn't come.

23:09.940 --> 23:11.460
Just you alone?

23:13.400 --> 23:14.350
Nie Yucheng.

23:15.610 --> 23:17.370
Mom, I'm going in.

23:18.640 --> 23:19.640
It'll be fine.

23:19.920 --> 23:21.650
I'll be right outside waiting.

23:21.800 --> 23:22.490
Okay, I know.

23:22.490 --> 23:23.220
Don't worry.

23:23.320 --> 23:24.390
Here, take your phone.

23:24.390 --> 23:25.540
Go on in.

23:26.810 --> 23:27.500
Coming.

23:36.970 --> 23:37.550
[Purong Hotel Exam Week Promotion Plan]

23:37.570 --> 23:38.520
[Campaign Background]

23:38.550 --> 23:40.630
[Customized Services][Exclusive Floors
for Exam Families]

23:39.200 --> 23:39.880
Mr. Wei said

23:39.880 --> 23:41.400
this plan works perfectly

23:40.660 --> 23:41.860
[Nutritious Set Meals]

23:41.420 --> 23:42.190
for Kuanli Hotel too.

23:42.190 --> 23:43.790
Please take a look, Mr. Duan.

23:47.110 --> 23:48.200
Ji Feng,

23:48.640 --> 23:50.310
you'll never guess.

23:50.310 --> 23:51.440
All your hard work

23:51.440 --> 23:53.480
ended up handing me a huge opportunity.

23:53.480 --> 23:55.650
Revise this plan quickly

23:55.680 --> 23:57.640
and send it to our senior
management group.

23:57.640 --> 23:58.920
Make sure my dad sees it.

23:58.920 --> 23:59.510
Got it.

23:59.530 --> 24:01.920
Are we still sticking with Dianjiangchun
for the live stream?

24:01.920 --> 24:03.550
Should we find a new host instead?

24:03.550 --> 24:04.830
Keep Dianjiangchun.

24:05.030 --> 24:06.110
She's the perfect ready-made option.

24:06.110 --> 24:07.840
But isn't she Ji Feng's person?

24:09.110 --> 24:11.650
You underestimate Ms. Jiang.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.550
She answers to no one.

24:19.210 --> 24:19.860
Sis,

24:20.020 --> 24:21.750
it's Young Mr. Duan on the line.

24:28.520 --> 24:29.510
Hello, Mr. Duan.

24:29.720 --> 24:32.070
I thought Dianjiangchun
and our Kuanli Group

24:32.070 --> 24:33.690
were long-term strategic partners.

24:33.690 --> 24:35.550
Last time you hosted the Song
Banquet Chinese Gala

24:35.550 --> 24:36.790
at our hotel,

24:36.900 --> 24:39.600
the view count went through the roof.

24:39.620 --> 24:42.200
Why leave us out this time?

24:43.200 --> 24:44.720
No need for such harsh words.

24:44.720 --> 24:46.480
Our team has always hoped

24:46.480 --> 24:48.310
to deepen cooperation with Kuanli.

24:48.310 --> 24:49.840
Since you said it yourself,

24:49.960 --> 24:51.450
I'll cut to the chase.

24:51.470 --> 24:52.310
Kuanli is launching

24:52.310 --> 24:55.270
an exam room promotion soon.

24:55.400 --> 24:56.880
I'm wondering if Ms. Jiang

24:56.880 --> 24:58.880
could lend us a hand.

25:00.920 --> 25:02.000
I know

25:02.000 --> 25:03.400
your contract with Purong

25:03.400 --> 25:05.030
still hasn't been finalized.

25:05.030 --> 25:06.720
Hear our offer first.

25:06.850 --> 25:08.710
If you're willing to work with us,

25:08.880 --> 25:09.810
Duan Aoxiang always plays fair.

25:09.810 --> 25:10.880
Let's have an

25:10.920 --> 25:12.680
honest competition.

25:13.400 --> 25:14.160
Sure.

25:14.510 --> 25:16.040
When would you like to meet?

25:16.270 --> 25:17.110
Right now.

25:17.770 --> 25:18.830
Send me your address.

25:18.830 --> 25:19.550
No need.

25:19.960 --> 25:20.820
My car's parked

25:20.880 --> 25:22.940
right outside your office building.

25:25.310 --> 25:25.840
Alright,

25:26.220 --> 25:27.180
I'm on my way.

25:37.260 --> 25:38.180
Zhenzhen,

25:39.640 --> 25:41.350
don't stress too much.

25:41.440 --> 25:42.690
[Shanghai Hongkou District
Central Hospital]

25:42.640 --> 25:45.680
The doctor said there's still hope.

25:42.710 --> 25:43.900
[Pathological Diagnosis Report]

25:46.550 --> 25:47.880
Our Yucheng

25:48.680 --> 25:50.590
still has a chance.

26:10.590 --> 26:11.670
Door unlocked.

26:11.700 --> 26:13.230
Hello, your food delivery.

26:15.880 --> 26:16.830
Takeout again,

26:16.830 --> 26:17.760
always takeout.

26:17.880 --> 26:19.440
Is it really that hard
to cook

26:19.440 --> 26:20.770
a proper meal for my son?

26:57.030 --> 26:57.830
Ms. Xu.

26:57.920 --> 27:00.480
word is Kuanli Hotel across the street
is also launching exam week promotions.

27:00.480 --> 27:01.200
Really?

27:01.730 --> 27:02.930
How did you hear that?

27:03.160 --> 27:05.550
A girl from the lobby bar said.

27:05.740 --> 27:06.550
She accidentally

27:06.550 --> 27:08.830
overheard Young Mr. Duan
on the phone yesterday

27:08.830 --> 27:11.090
and got chewed out badly.

27:11.180 --> 27:13.640
He mentioned Kuanli just

27:13.640 --> 27:15.680
signed a top streamer

27:15.680 --> 27:17.480
for their exam season campaign.

27:18.830 --> 27:19.640
Ms. Xu,

27:19.980 --> 27:21.960
isn't this suspicious?

27:21.990 --> 27:24.510
We just finalized our exam week plan,

27:24.510 --> 27:26.680
and Kuanli copies us right away.

27:27.440 --> 27:28.160
Eat first.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.700
I'll go check this out.

27:35.030 --> 27:35.440
Mr. Ji,

27:35.440 --> 27:36.160
the Sales Department

27:36.160 --> 27:37.790
pulled an all-nighter
to finish this live stream contract.

27:37.790 --> 27:39.070
Mr. Qian has already reviewed it.

27:39.070 --> 27:40.130
Please take a look.

27:40.720 --> 27:42.110
These are our online marketing plans

27:42.110 --> 27:43.550
to support the live event.

27:43.550 --> 27:44.830
Please review them as well.

27:44.830 --> 27:45.750
And these

27:45.750 --> 27:47.000
offline promotion materials drafted

27:47.000 --> 27:48.710
by the Communications Team
on Mr. Qian's request.

27:48.710 --> 27:49.880
Kindly check for revisions.

27:49.880 --> 27:51.610
and see if there are any issues.

27:52.110 --> 27:53.920
Is Mr. Qian in his office?

27:53.920 --> 27:55.030
Mr. Qian is...

27:56.880 --> 27:57.680
Mr. Ji,

27:57.880 --> 27:59.030
you were looking for me?

27:59.030 --> 28:00.450
Speak of the devil.

28:00.640 --> 28:01.350
Come in,

28:01.350 --> 28:02.010
take a seat.

28:09.200 --> 28:10.590
It seems the Sales Department

28:10.590 --> 28:13.250
takes this live stream project
very seriously.

28:13.310 --> 28:14.350
You put together

28:14.350 --> 28:16.830
such thorough reports in no time.

28:17.510 --> 28:18.790
Great work.

28:19.110 --> 28:20.160
Mr. Ji.

28:20.160 --> 28:21.350
To be honest,

28:21.530 --> 28:23.300
I know next to nothing

28:23.330 --> 28:24.640
about livestreaming.

28:24.640 --> 28:26.520
I'm totally old-school.

28:26.880 --> 28:27.880
Luckily,

28:27.880 --> 28:30.800
one of my team members stepped up.

28:31.350 --> 28:33.190
very document you see today

28:33.350 --> 28:35.640
was single-handedly done by her.

28:36.110 --> 28:37.070
Otherwise,

28:37.070 --> 28:38.960
I'd have nothing to present.

28:39.640 --> 28:41.590
Who's this unsung hero?

28:42.110 --> 28:43.350
Lu Zhenzhen.

28:46.880 --> 28:47.720
Mr. Ji,

28:48.350 --> 28:49.990
forgive me for saying so.

28:50.390 --> 28:51.990
Lu Zhenzhen.

28:52.110 --> 28:52.680
Yes?

28:52.920 --> 28:53.650
She's young,

28:53.880 --> 28:56.880
and sometimes reckless,

28:56.900 --> 28:58.470
but there's no denying

28:58.680 --> 28:59.480
she's capable

28:59.750 --> 29:00.830
and driven.

29:01.680 --> 29:02.830
Don't you agree?

29:05.030 --> 29:06.360
Have some tea, Mr. Qian.

29:09.210 --> 29:10.320
Of course,

29:10.720 --> 29:13.540
I don't want to overpraise my staff.

29:13.640 --> 29:16.260
But livestreaming

29:16.660 --> 29:18.340
is brand-new territory

29:18.370 --> 29:20.310
for Purong.

29:20.720 --> 29:23.000
If you're looking for someone

29:23.030 --> 29:25.640
experienced and reliable,

29:26.510 --> 29:29.070
Ms. Lu is the perfect candidate.

29:29.960 --> 29:31.890
Thank you for the recommendation.

29:32.350 --> 29:33.960
I've noticed Ms. Lu's

29:33.960 --> 29:35.360
outstanding performance.

29:35.360 --> 29:36.160
Rest assured.

29:36.160 --> 29:37.110
Great,

29:42.710 --> 29:44.030
this tea is excellent.

29:48.620 --> 29:50.510
Secretary Wu, I need to see
Mr. Ji urgently.

29:50.510 --> 29:51.200
Do you have an appointment?

29:51.200 --> 29:52.260
Good day, Mr. Qian.

29:54.200 --> 29:55.100
Mr. Qian.

29:59.270 --> 30:00.030
What's wrong?

30:00.030 --> 30:01.200
Kuanli

30:01.270 --> 30:03.200
is copying our exam week campaign?

30:03.750 --> 30:05.150
Where did this come from?

30:05.310 --> 30:06.400
One of the lobby bar staff

30:06.400 --> 30:08.400
overheard Mr. Duan's private call.

30:20.110 --> 30:20.790
Brother,

30:21.000 --> 30:22.060
It's pouring rain,

30:27.240 --> 30:28.640
and he's out running.

30:29.580 --> 30:31.110
Always worrying people sick.

30:31.110 --> 30:31.950
Jeez.

31:08.460 --> 31:09.560
Take a look.

31:08.590 --> 31:13.070
[Live Stream Cooperation Proposal
Exam Week Promotion]

31:17.430 --> 31:19.270
I haven't signed our contract yet,

31:19.270 --> 31:21.330
but I can't hold them off much longer.

31:21.680 --> 31:23.260
Duan Aoxiang is offering

31:23.280 --> 31:25.310
the streamer
a 40% revenue split —

31:25.640 --> 31:27.400
the highest rate in the industry.

31:27.400 --> 31:28.480
Our board now prefers

31:28.480 --> 31:30.630
letting your two hotels compete
head-to-head.

31:30.630 --> 31:32.690
This puts you at a huge disadvantage.

31:32.830 --> 31:33.960
As long as Purong

31:33.960 --> 31:35.480
gets to join the competition.

31:35.480 --> 31:37.540
But what if they cut you out entirely?

31:38.570 --> 31:41.420
My team is being pushed to
prioritize Kuanli first,

31:41.420 --> 31:42.850
streaming their promotion

31:42.850 --> 31:43.990
before yours.

31:44.110 --> 31:45.420
Can you accept that?

31:47.590 --> 31:48.440
I accept.

31:48.790 --> 31:50.020
You're really okay with this?

31:50.020 --> 31:52.560
All your early research
and promotion costs

31:52.590 --> 31:54.480
will only benefit Kuanli.

31:54.510 --> 31:56.510
They're reaping all your hard work.

31:59.350 --> 32:00.550
What if I run

32:00.670 --> 32:02.190
an extra live stream for you

32:02.190 --> 32:03.550
the day before their broadcast,

32:03.550 --> 32:04.550
using my personal backup account?

32:04.550 --> 32:05.200
No.

32:05.480 --> 32:06.640
That would break industry rules.

32:06.640 --> 32:08.550
But they stole our idea first.

32:16.270 --> 32:17.550
Let me ask you one thing.

32:17.550 --> 32:20.550
Was Duan Aoxiang your main contact?

32:28.640 --> 32:31.300
Mr. Ji, did you approve
letting Kuanli go first?

32:31.330 --> 32:32.120
I did.

32:33.340 --> 32:34.200
You knew perfectly well

32:34.200 --> 32:36.070
they copied our concept.

32:36.070 --> 32:37.820
If they launch ahead of us,

32:37.850 --> 32:39.570
all our effort will be for nothing.

32:39.570 --> 32:40.570
It won't be wasted.

32:40.570 --> 32:42.490
No single hotel can

32:42.510 --> 32:44.800
monopolize this business.

32:45.550 --> 32:47.070
Let them take the lead,

32:47.070 --> 32:48.000
build momentum,

32:48.000 --> 32:49.310
heat up the market.

32:49.340 --> 32:51.340
Then we step in and ride the wave.

32:51.360 --> 32:52.270
It works in our favor.

32:52.270 --> 32:53.340
Are you serious?

32:53.360 --> 32:54.640
How many high-end hotel bookings

32:54.640 --> 32:56.460
can we realistically get
for exam families?

32:56.460 --> 32:58.110
If they take the first slice,

32:58.110 --> 32:59.880
there'll be nothing left for us.

32:59.880 --> 33:01.440
But the truth is,

33:01.680 --> 33:04.280
Dianjiangchun's contract
restricts her from

33:04.450 --> 33:05.720
breaking terms with Kuanli.

33:05.720 --> 33:08.350
So you'd sacrifice Purong's interests

33:08.350 --> 33:11.480
just to keep one streamer from breaking a deal?

33:08.390 --> 33:10.980
[General Manager's Office]

33:12.470 --> 33:15.500
[General Manager's Office]

33:22.350 --> 33:23.270
Do you trust me?

33:27.440 --> 33:29.520
Ms. Lu landed another big project?

33:30.270 --> 33:31.790
Dinner treat soon, Zhenzhen?

33:31.790 --> 33:32.550
I'm swamped.

33:32.550 --> 33:33.640
No time for treats.

33:34.030 --> 33:36.440
Quietly making big money, huh.

33:37.550 --> 33:38.590
Fine fine,

33:38.590 --> 33:41.450
I'll treat everyone to dinner
and karaoke tonight.

33:41.550 --> 33:43.270
Hey, party tonight?

33:43.270 --> 33:44.400
Everyone's invited if you're free.

33:44.400 --> 33:46.270
-Count me in.
-Thanks, Zhenzhen.

33:51.070 --> 33:51.330
[Mom]

33:53.770 --> 33:55.960
[Mom]

33:55.990 --> 33:57.020
[Incoming call rejected]

34:37.110 --> 34:38.449
Door unlocked.

34:40.280 --> 34:41.810
Mom, why are you still here?

34:42.070 --> 34:43.030
I've been waiting for you

34:43.030 --> 34:45.030
to talk about Yucheng's surgery.

34:45.550 --> 34:47.610
Why are you working overtime so late?

34:52.320 --> 34:53.630
Where were you working?

34:53.630 --> 34:55.000
You smell like hot pot.

34:55.070 --> 34:56.130
I ordered takeout.

35:07.510 --> 35:08.670
This surgery slot

35:08.670 --> 35:11.440
was only secured through connections
by Yucheng's father.

35:11.440 --> 35:13.510
You have to take time off work.

35:14.650 --> 35:15.540
[Surgery Informed Consent Form]

35:15.540 --> 35:17.110
[Medical]

35:16.280 --> 35:17.510
The day after tomorrow?

35:17.510 --> 35:18.550
I have to work the day after tomorrow.

35:18.550 --> 35:19.800
Just ask for leave.

35:19.840 --> 35:21.840
Yucheng needs hospitalization and surgery,

35:21.840 --> 35:24.040
there's endless paperwork to sort out.

35:24.450 --> 35:26.700
Mom, I really can't.

35:27.280 --> 35:29.110
I have a critical live stream that day,

35:29.110 --> 35:30.280
and I have to supervise the whole thing.

35:30.280 --> 35:31.800
What's a live stream compared to this?

35:31.800 --> 35:33.590
Your husband's going into surgery!

35:33.590 --> 35:35.450
Can't you tell what matters more?

35:36.350 --> 35:38.480
If this surgery
can truly heal Yucheng

35:38.480 --> 35:39.480
and let him

35:39.480 --> 35:40.920
go back to work,

35:41.070 --> 35:43.760
I'll resign on the spot to
take care of him full-time.

35:43.760 --> 35:45.630
But if there's no real
guarantee of recovery,

35:45.630 --> 35:47.480
why do we all keep draining each other?

35:47.480 --> 35:49.280
Why not just mind our
own duties?

35:49.960 --> 35:51.280
"Own duties"?

35:51.300 --> 35:52.420
Let me ask you.

35:52.450 --> 35:53.890
Since my son fell ill,

35:53.920 --> 35:55.630
have you fulfilled your duties as a wife?

35:55.630 --> 35:57.480
Have you taken care of his daily life?

35:57.480 --> 35:59.880
What exactly have you done
for this family?

36:00.670 --> 36:02.760
I'm the one bringing
in the income.

36:02.840 --> 36:04.110
I'm out working every day, pregnant,

36:04.110 --> 36:05.440
coming home late every night.

36:05.440 --> 36:06.360
Do you think I want this life?

36:06.360 --> 36:07.710
With Nie Yucheng like this now,

36:07.710 --> 36:08.550
If I stop working

36:08.550 --> 36:09.550
and earning now,

36:09.550 --> 36:11.190
how will this family survive?

36:11.190 --> 36:12.630
Empty words.

36:13.230 --> 36:15.290
Do you really pay for this household?

36:15.440 --> 36:17.000
Everything my son earned

36:17.000 --> 36:18.400
fed you, clothed you,

36:18.400 --> 36:19.590
bought your school-district apartment,

36:19.590 --> 36:21.110
and paid for your premium

36:21.130 --> 36:22.320
maternity hospital.

36:22.320 --> 36:23.580
That's all in the past.

36:24.230 --> 36:26.840
The maternity center deposit
was fully refunded.

36:26.840 --> 36:29.170
All our savings went to his medical bills.

36:29.840 --> 36:31.550
Did you ever ask me?

36:31.550 --> 36:32.750
Did I ever agree all these?

36:32.750 --> 36:34.100
Did you ever discuss this with me?

36:34.100 --> 36:34.950
This...

36:35.080 --> 36:36.850
Discuss what?

36:37.070 --> 36:39.440
When family is sick, saving
them comes first.

36:39.440 --> 36:40.240
What about me?

36:42.030 --> 36:44.090
Do I have to sacrifice my whole future

36:44.510 --> 36:45.930
to live an exhausted half-life?

36:45.930 --> 36:47.920
An exhausted half-life?

36:48.030 --> 36:49.480
Watch your mouth.

36:49.480 --> 36:51.190
I'll slap some sense into you.

36:51.190 --> 36:52.440
Try me.

36:52.910 --> 36:53.790
Let me tell you,

36:54.230 --> 36:55.840
This is my home now.

36:55.860 --> 36:57.040
Get out.

36:57.630 --> 36:59.400
Leave right now.

36:59.960 --> 37:00.880
Get out!

37:12.810 --> 37:15.140
Blood… you're bleeding.

37:15.550 --> 37:16.760
My grandson!

37:16.880 --> 37:18.110
My grandson!

37:25.590 --> 37:27.220
[Hotel Detailed Management]

37:27.380 --> 37:29.720
[The characteristics of hotel
corporate culture]

37:39.270 --> 37:40.020
Mr. Ji,

37:42.030 --> 37:43.160
I need to talk to you.

37:43.990 --> 37:44.800
Sure.

37:54.150 --> 37:55.070
Help!

37:57.440 --> 37:58.590
Somebody!

37:59.670 --> 38:00.920
What's wrong?

38:01.650 --> 38:02.650
Where's my baby?

38:02.790 --> 38:04.590
Your baby's in the neonatal ICU.

38:05.360 --> 38:06.470
And my family?

38:06.890 --> 38:08.990
They're all with the baby.

38:11.550 --> 38:13.190
Your little one is premature,

38:13.190 --> 38:14.840
very fragile right now.

38:16.030 --> 38:17.690
I want to transfer hospitals.

38:18.330 --> 38:20.850
I can't help with that.

38:20.880 --> 38:21.840
Wait till the doctor's here.

38:21.840 --> 38:23.700
You'll need to talk to the doctor.

38:24.250 --> 38:25.340
Please leave.

38:25.920 --> 38:28.030
Your bed pad needs changing.

38:28.030 --> 38:30.960
-Untreated lochia will make you sick.
-I said leave!

38:31.710 --> 38:32.550
Now.

38:38.090 --> 38:39.160
Excuse me,

38:39.180 --> 38:40.660
could I borrow this stool?

38:43.180 --> 38:44.450
Thank you.

38:55.890 --> 38:58.870
[Lobby Lounge]

38:56.650 --> 38:58.230
Our Sales rep for

38:58.520 --> 38:59.480
tomorrow's live stream

38:59.480 --> 39:00.880
has a last-minute emergency.

39:00.880 --> 39:02.040
Who is it?

39:02.070 --> 39:02.910
Lu Zhenzhen.

39:03.690 --> 39:04.820
What happened?

39:05.480 --> 39:06.920
She's been admitted to hospital.

39:06.920 --> 39:08.570
We don't know the full details yet,

39:08.570 --> 39:10.410
but she definitely can't make it tomorrow.

39:10.410 --> 39:11.500
What do we do about the live stream then?

39:11.500 --> 39:12.570
That's why I came to find you.

39:12.570 --> 39:13.480
I think

39:13.920 --> 39:15.480
you're the perfect person to take over.

39:15.480 --> 39:16.320
Me?

39:16.760 --> 39:17.940
I know nothing about sales.

39:17.940 --> 39:18.940
You don't need to.

39:20.030 --> 39:22.190
Though the Purong Hotel
exam-week promotion

39:22.190 --> 39:23.670
falls under

39:23.670 --> 39:24.930
the Sales Department,

39:24.930 --> 39:25.560
but

39:25.590 --> 39:28.400
you're the one who created this project
from the start.

39:28.400 --> 39:29.590
You handled all the research,

39:29.590 --> 39:32.470
planning and internal proposals.

39:32.840 --> 39:33.760
You know

39:33.760 --> 39:35.490
every detail of this campaign,

39:35.760 --> 39:36.820
and you understand

39:36.920 --> 39:38.450
exactly what parents need.

39:39.030 --> 39:42.110
You're also the one who convinced me

39:42.880 --> 39:44.480
to launch this online promotion.

39:44.480 --> 39:45.230
I believe

39:45.380 --> 39:46.770
You're far better than Ms. Lu

39:46.770 --> 39:48.480
at presenting its true value.

39:52.230 --> 39:53.070
Alright,

39:53.710 --> 39:54.590
I'll try.

39:56.840 --> 39:59.110
But I need two favors.

39:59.920 --> 40:01.440
First,

40:01.440 --> 40:02.400
please arrange

40:02.400 --> 40:04.030
a temporary lobby manager

40:04.030 --> 40:05.290
to cover my shift here.

40:05.480 --> 40:07.190
Second…

40:07.190 --> 40:09.650
Take over the Jazz Bar
performance tonight.

40:11.730 --> 40:13.260
I'll get everything ready.

40:18.630 --> 40:19.890
After the live stream…

40:20.360 --> 40:21.480
I have something to say to you.
